Setup an Active directory
Now set IP address on linux machine
Set gateway
Set DNS
Set search domain
Set hostname of workstation/server
Set time

Realm:

#realm -v discover onwire.lab


#yum install 'sssd\|adcli\|oddjob\|samba-common\'

 #realm -v join onwire.lab

After joining AD now get tkhan@onwire.lab user

#getent passwd tkhan@onwire.lab

To give sudoers rights:

#tkhan@onwire.lab or onwire\tkhan All=(All)